'''Christiane Chabi-Kao''' (wavutse ku ya 30 Kamena 1963) ni umuyobozi wa filime wo muri [[Bénine]] akaba n'umwanditsi.

== Ubuzima ==
Chabi-Kao yavukiye i Marseille mu [[Bufaransa]] mu 1963.  Yize muri Kaminuza ya Reims Champagne-Ardenne kuva 1984 kugeza 1986. Mu 1990, Chabi-Kao yasubiye muri [[Afurika]].  Yasohokanye na filime ye ya mbere, ''Les enfants esclaves'', mu 2005, documentaire isobanura abana b'abacakara bigezweho. 

Mu 2007, yayoboye filime ''Les inseparables''. Ivuga amateka y'abavandimwe Yawa na Abi, se bamugurisha ku mucuruza w'abana, maze nyina ajya mu ishami rishinzwe kurengera abana rya Polisi kugira ngo amenye uko byagenze. Iyi filime yakozwe na UNICEF na Radiyo na Televiziyo y'igihugu ya [[Bénin]] (ORTB), isohoka nk'uruhererekane rwa firime enye. Chabi-Kao yanditse iyi filime mu rwego rwo gukangurira no guhagarika icuruzwa ry'abana.  Yakiriye igihembo nyafurika Numerique mu iserukiramuco rya Vues d'Afrique ryabereye i Montreal mu 2008, anahabwa igihembo cy’uburenganzira bwa muntu mu iserukiramuco rya Filimi na Televiziyo rya Panafrican 2009 rya Ouagadougou.  Nyuma yo kumenyeshwa itegeko ribuza kwerekanwa ku buntu, Chabi-Kao yateguye kwerekana filime ku banyeshuri 300 ba Burkinabe. 

Mu 2009, yasimbuye Monique Mbeke Phoba nk'umuyobozi w'ikirori cya Lagunimages i Cotonou .  Nkumuyobozi, Chabi-Kao afasha kwambara iserukiramuco rya firime ryizina rimwe.  Yakoreye iserukiramuco imyaka itari mike mbere yo kuba umuyobozi, ahabwa inkunga na Deutsche Welle Academy yo kwiga uko bategura ibirori. 

Chabi-Kao yanditse akanayobora ibiganiro bya televiziyo ''bigizwe n'ibice 14'' muri Les Chenapans muri 2013. Irerekana ubuzima nintambara byingimbi batanu bo muri Bénin, kandi ikoresha abakinnyi badafite umwuga. 

